Rating: 4
I have made this recipe many times - we really like the taste. I had a problem keeping the patties together until I discovered that placing them in a single layer on a tray covered with plastic wrap and refrigerating for a while does it. Just lift up one end of the wrap and flip the patty on to a spatula, and flop onto the pan. This flip-flop also works great for vegetable pancakes.

